<item>
            <title>[DERBY-1965] NetworkServerControlImpl never closes the socket or streams it opens in setUpSocket.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-1965</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Every method that calls setUpSocket should have a  call to a new closeSocket() method.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12353335">DERBY-1965</key>
            <summary>NetworkServerControlImpl never closes the socket or streams it opens in setUpSocket.</summary>
